metadata.name: In the Name of Digital Renaissance
metadata.description:
God's creation of the world and of animal, animals fall from grace and punishment up until the birth of Meditation Rabbit, the savior of animals.

In the Name of Digital Renaissance or The Last Judgment is a fresco by the Ukrainian Renaissance painter Alexis Olin covering the whole altar wall of the Sistine Chapel in Vatican City.

***

On permanent display at the digital part of Louvre, Paris since 2022
5082 x 5643 pixels
